data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. If you want to live in a safe, quiet community, then this is your home! This home has a NEW DIMENTIONAL ROOF!!! AIR CONDITIONER FROM 2021, BEAUTIFUL PORCELAIN TILE throughout the ENTIRE HOUSE, REMODELED MAIN BATHROOM. This lovely home offers 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, and a 2-car Garage, with a LARGE FENCED BACK YARD and COVERED LANAI. The main bedroom has a walk-in closet and a beautifully remodeled bathroom. It has two more nice-sized bedrooms with a bathroom in between. The kitchen has all wood cabinets, granite countertops, and stainless steel appliances. The great room has plenty of room for entertaining friends and family. This lovely home is located in the South Fork Community and offers a resort-style pool, Jacuzzi, tennis courts, playground, and more in the heart of Riverview. You will be minutes away from shopping, dining, U.S. 301, I-75, and the Selman Expressway. Plenty of grocery stores like Publix, Sprouts, Sam's Club, and Walmart exist. Close to St. Joseph's Hospital, Bay Care, and the VA Hospital. Take I-75 to Siesta Key Beach or Ana Maria Beach, or shop at Ellington Mall. Schedule your private showing today!
